1
00:00:58,439 --> 00:00:59,880
Our village has been exposed.

2
00:01:00,320 --> 00:01:01,840
Demon hunters will come again.

3
00:01:02,799 --> 00:01:03,960
If you hesitate,

4
00:01:04,399 --> 00:01:06,840
our clan will be wiped out.

5
00:01:07,519 --> 00:01:09,280
Don't make another mistake.

6
00:01:35,319 --> 00:01:36,120
A'Li,

7
00:01:36,879 --> 00:01:37,879
do you remember?

8
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:40,519
That year,

9
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,599
I ran out of the temple,

10
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,439
and you were waiting under the tree.

11
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:47,519
Petals were falling,

12
00:01:48,239 --> 00:01:49,959
but you smiled at me.

13
00:01:50,959 --> 00:01:52,680
[I thought,]

14
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:54,799
[I, Shen Daozhi,]

15
00:01:55,959 --> 00:01:57,439
[have nothing more to wish for in life,]

16
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,200
[only to grow old]

17
00:02:01,959 --> 00:02:03,319
[with A'Li.]

18
00:02:12,439 --> 00:02:13,599
[I also wondered,]

19
00:02:14,120 --> 00:02:15,360
[if that spring]

20
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:16,800
[could have lasted a bit longer,]

21
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,159
[and the peach blossoms remained,]

22
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:21,719
[could we have said a proper goodbye?]

23
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:25,159
[If we had said goodbye properly,]

24
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,960
[could we have truly met again?]

25
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:34,599
[Love is endless.]

26
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:38,000
[But I'm glad]

27
00:02:38,759 --> 00:02:39,759
[I met you,]

28
00:02:40,479 --> 00:02:41,360
[and got to know you.]

29
00:02:43,199 --> 00:02:45,000
[To meet you again in this life]

30
00:02:45,439 --> 00:02:46,919
[is a blessing.]

31
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:49,280
[Growing old together is irreplaceable.]

32
00:02:50,319 --> 00:02:51,719
[If this is fate,]

33
00:02:53,199 --> 00:02:55,199
[then it's the best ending for us.]

34
00:03:02,479 --> 00:03:03,080
[For you,]

35
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:05,199
[I'm willing to do anything.]

36
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:10,719
A'Li,

37
00:03:11,479 --> 00:03:12,919
I'm exhausted today.

38
00:03:15,479 --> 00:03:16,759
I'll go to sleep first.

39
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,360
[A'Li,]

40
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,639
[no matter how many times we reincarnate,]

41
00:05:40,600 --> 00:05:42,360
[I will still love you.]

42
00:05:43,959 --> 00:05:44,959
[For you,]

43
00:05:45,519 --> 00:05:46,759
[I'm willing to do anything.]

44
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,600
[Qingdu Temple has assembled.]

45
00:05:59,759 --> 00:06:01,360
[We must retrieve the Spiritual Root today.]

46
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:26,439
[A'Li,]

47
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:29,319
[I made a wish in my past life]

48
00:06:30,519 --> 00:06:31,920
[to see you every day,]

49
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,839
[and be with you for all my life.]

50
00:06:34,839 --> 00:06:36,560
[Though it's been a bumpy road,]

51
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,959
[we've been together in two lives.]

52
00:06:39,839 --> 00:06:40,759
[This wish]

53
00:06:41,759 --> 00:06:42,839
[has come true.]

54
00:06:44,439 --> 00:06:45,240
[Today,]

55
00:06:46,240 --> 00:06:47,160
[I make another wish.]

56
00:06:47,839 --> 00:06:49,480
[May you live a hundred years without worries,]

57
00:06:50,439 --> 00:06:51,720
[healthy and happy.]

58
00:06:52,519 --> 00:06:53,560
[I wish]

59
00:06:55,759 --> 00:06:56,800
[to never see Meng Li]

60
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,319
[again in this life.]

61
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:13,360
Shen Que's condition

62
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:15,759
indicates his Spiritual Root was hidden.

63
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:17,439
Extracting it

64
00:07:17,439 --> 00:07:18,839
directly

65
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:20,680
would damage his Primordial Spirit

66
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:21,680
and kill him instantly.

67
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,920
Extracting the Spiritual Root

68
00:07:29,279 --> 00:07:30,519
could kill you.

69
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,399
Li,

70
00:07:33,959 --> 00:07:36,079
you have more important things to do.

71
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,120
Li!

72
00:08:46,039 --> 00:08:48,480
Evil spirits have hidden among us for years.

73
00:08:49,000 --> 00:08:49,720
Today,

74
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:51,960
we've finally located the Demon Village!

75
00:08:53,080 --> 00:08:54,960
All disciples of Qingdu Temple,

76
00:08:55,120 --> 00:08:56,519
purge the evil spirits,

77
00:08:56,679 --> 00:08:57,720
and restore peace to the world!

78
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:58,879
Form the array!

79
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,919
Demon hunters killed demons without cause,

80
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:08,279
leaving us homeless,

81
00:09:08,679 --> 00:09:09,720
forced to eke out a living here.

82
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,879
We fight for survival,

83
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,679
just trying to live,

84
00:09:13,879 --> 00:09:14,879
what's wrong with that?

85
00:09:15,799 --> 00:09:17,080
[We may be weak,]

86
00:09:17,879 --> 00:09:20,519
[but we won't just wait to die!]

87
00:09:32,679 --> 00:09:34,639
[The time has come.]

88
00:09:35,080 --> 00:09:38,639
[Today, we'll restore our souls.]

89
00:09:40,879 --> 00:09:42,679
[The blazing furnace,]

90
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:45,000
[the world turns to fire.]

91
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,799
[Netherworld Soul Capture,]

92
00:09:57,799 --> 00:09:59,279
[demons and devils in chaos.]

93
00:09:59,279 --> 00:10:00,600
[The Three Pure Bells ring,]

94
00:10:00,879 --> 00:10:02,000
[and all will be captured.]

95
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:38,360
The barrier didn't break?

96
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:40,120
How could this be?

97
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,399
You killed my people,

98
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:12,799
and bullied my companions.

99
00:11:13,320 --> 00:11:14,399
You reap what you sow.

100
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:15,360
Today,

101
00:11:15,919 --> 00:11:17,679
I'll repay you in blood.

102
00:11:17,799 --> 00:11:19,159
All demons are the same.

103
00:11:19,879 --> 00:11:21,360
They all bluff.

104
00:11:29,519 --> 00:11:30,159
Fine.

105
00:11:30,799 --> 00:11:32,240
Everything that happens next

106
00:11:33,279 --> 00:11:34,679
is your retribution.

107
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:46,799
How could this be?

108
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:48,600
No.

109
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,159
It's a dream.

110
00:11:52,879 --> 00:11:53,759
Celestial Platform Stars,

111
00:11:53,840 --> 00:11:54,919
respond to the invisible.

112
00:11:54,919 --> 00:11:55,799
Three Souls Eternal,

113
00:11:55,799 --> 00:11:57,519
bring you back to reality.

114
00:11:57,519 --> 00:11:58,320
Breaking the Dreamless Clarity,

115
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,120
awaken from the dream.

116
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,840
The spell didn't work on you?

117
00:12:07,159 --> 00:12:08,120
What is a dream?

118
00:12:08,759 --> 00:12:10,000
What is reality?

119
00:12:10,559 --> 00:12:11,639
Can you tell the difference?

120
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:18,600
You've done evil for years.

121
00:12:18,919 --> 00:12:21,799
Today, I've found your hideout.

122
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:24,879
I'll wipe out every last one of you

123
00:12:24,879 --> 00:12:26,519
evil demons!

124
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,519
Evil?

125
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:30,759
You slaughter your own kind

126
00:12:30,759 --> 00:12:32,000
and drive us from our homes.

127
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,440
We're forced to live in this forsaken place.

128
00:12:34,159 --> 00:12:36,000
And you call that just?

129
00:12:36,519 --> 00:12:37,600
We fight for survival,

130
00:12:37,600 --> 00:12:38,519
simply trying to live.

131
00:12:38,519 --> 00:12:39,600
What's wrong with that?

132
00:12:40,120 --> 00:12:40,960
We demons

133
00:12:41,399 --> 00:12:43,799
are no ordinary beings to be captured.

134
00:13:00,559 --> 00:13:01,559
I've said it before,

135
00:13:01,960 --> 00:13:02,720
today,

136
00:13:03,399 --> 00:13:05,360
I'll make you pay

137
00:13:05,519 --> 00:13:08,120
for your sins.

138
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,159
Remember,

139
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:21,879
this time I spared your life.

140
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:23,960
Take everything you've seen and heard,

141
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:25,919
every thought and idea back to your temple.

142
00:13:25,919 --> 00:13:27,600
Tell everyone in Qingdu Temple,

143
00:13:28,399 --> 00:13:30,519
if anyone dares to harm my clan again,

144
00:13:30,879 --> 00:13:33,440
I'll make them suffer and die in disgrace.

145
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,000
I, Meng Li,

146
00:13:35,279 --> 00:13:38,639
will keep my word.

147
00:13:51,519 --> 00:13:52,679
With the spiritual root restored,

148
00:13:54,759 --> 00:13:57,000
mortals will never harm us again.
